dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Adams County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature dataclass within the geodatabase Adams_Roads_YE2016.gdb. [Adams County Streets - Attribute table is formatted for use by the Spillman emergency dispatch system and the ESRI Alphanumeric geocoder. Metadata is minimal, only the attribute descriptions have been recorded. TG 20090910]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
